ion on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.45633, "shard": "04", "shelf_id": "sn86076249, 1908-06-24, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/nvln", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["newspapers", "white pine", "nevada", "ely", "united states", "ely (nev.)"], "subject_headings": ["Ely (Nev.)--Newspapers", "Nevada--Ely", "United States--Nevada--White Pine--Ely"], "subjects": [{"ely": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:ely&fo=json"}, {"ely (nev.)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:ely+%28nev.%29&fo=json"}, {"nevada": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:nevada&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}, {"white pine": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:white+pine&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2023-06-30T22:34:53.853Z", "title": "The White Pine news (Ely, Nev.), June 24, 1908", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn86076249/1908-06-24/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn86076249/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn86076249", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/1f524a17-f5ff-5890-952a-23f344cbaf86"], "batch": ["nvln_hiko_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1906", "description": ["Daily Vol. 1, no. 1 (Dec. 25, 1906)-v. 41, no. 240 (June 30, 1910). Title varies slightly as: White Pine daily news, June 26, 1907-Oct. 30, 1907. Saturday issues entitled: White Pine news daily edition and weekly mining review, Apr. 13-May 4, 1907; White Pine news Saturday edition, May 11-June 22, 1907; White Pine weekly news, Dec. 21-Dec. 28, 1907. Title from publisher's statement: Daily White Pine news, Dec. 25, 1906-Mar. 22, 1907. Resumes numbering of The White Pine news (Treasure City, Nev. : 1868) in 1909. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Issued also in weekly edition: White Pine news weekly mining review (1907), Jan. 12, 1907-Dec. 14, 1907; White Pine news weekly mining review (1909), Jan. 2, 1909-February 19, 1910. White Pine news weekly mining review (East Ely, Nev. : 1910) 2771-8123 (DLC)sn 86076354 (OCoLC)14066797"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:05.071Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-11", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-11"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn86076249/", "image_url": [], "index": 3, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [39.253136, -114.875111], "location": ["white pine", "nevada", "united states", "ely"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-114.875111, 39.253136], "number": ["13790203", "sn86076249", "sn86076355", "sn84022047", "1", "2025-07-01t13:40:36.900000", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn86076249/1906-12-25/ed-1/", "sn86076354", "2771-5515", "sn86076357", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn86076249/1910-06-30/ed-1/", "online resource", "original", "nevada state museum & historical society", "2023-06-27t19:21:13.388758", "univ of nevada, las vegas", "1083", "2026-04-13t21:30:13", "microfilm service copy"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Daily White Pine news", "White Pine daily news", "White Pine news daily edition and weekly mining review", "White Pine news Saturday edition", "White Pine weekly news"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "chronicling america", "catalog", "the white pine news (ely, nev.) 1906-1910", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 65.17704, "shelf_id": "Newspaper", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "usnd", "catalog"], "subject": ["newspapers", "white pine", "neva